><title>Still here. War is still raging. Appreciate all the international help though.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/chjLtIY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gDxuoiI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Morning coffee</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/R7R4rvB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Made a lot of fortifications lately</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HlCD71V.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s cozy, if not for mice running across my face at night.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XPDRUMP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My new pal</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1HxICFi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My mate with some gear we’ve got from volunteers</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zBHFLlE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This dude is almost 70. He’s the most efficient dude in our platoon.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lpYrsb4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>That’s why you shouldn’t buy cheap plates</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7XlAEfm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The weather is better each day. I’ve also been promoted to a Sargent. And I have 10 subordinates now.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ozlrSyc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I lived here for quite some time</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XygqFRS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pnOzC2E.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Some soup</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vUZswr9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My dumbbells(20 kg/44 lbs each)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YVISg4c.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Our dining place)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/84i281a.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>On a slightly more serious note. This my trophy from before. Intact russian mre. I am going to auction it, to buy some gear for my guys. But I have no clue how to do it. If there will be any suggestions – they’ll be very much appreciated.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/chjLtIY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[EliBLifter]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Animal videos #6</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mSldeH1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZliihTs.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Bo4bFiL.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PnVTK9C.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1IRpiWq.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fRzwcHm.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5fmah6v.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CFv2Hz9.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5EEnxid.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VtDiBM1.gif" style="ma